<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Moritz Auracher, Heinrich Frauhofer, Konrad Schwarzenberger und Hans Camerer</head><p>Der Rat bittet um vertrauliche und rasche Mitteilung wegen der Werbung von Truppen in Franken.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_33" id="15r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_33_r1l18">Moricʒen Auracher vnd <expan>heinr<ex>ichen</ex></expan> frauhofern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l19"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenern cʒu wertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns iſt fürware geſagt vnd cʒu wiſſen getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l21">worden / vvie daʒ gar groſʒ gewerb vnd
                                <expan>ſamnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> d </del> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l22">francken vnd danẏden v̈mb ſey / Begern wir von euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l23">daʒ Jr an dem Hauptman der euch
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l25">an <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wo Jr das erfaren mügt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_33_r1l24">wo Jr mügt </ab></add> ın geheime
                                <expan>vorſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<add><ab facs="#facs_33_line_1576652616472_1425">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd erfaren </del></ab></add>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l26">wöllet / <del rend="strikethrough">waʒ das gewerb ſeẏ
                            / vnd </del> wer das gewerb alſo tu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l27">vnd <del rend="strikethrough">waʒ </del> waʒ das
                        gewerbe ſeẏ / vnd auf wen / vnd waʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_line_1571130712639_256">Jr alſo ervorſchett oder erfaret das
                        lat vns <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>eygentlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_33_line_1571130702429_251">
<del rend="strikethrough">kürcʒlıchen </del></ab></add>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_line_1571130770182_280">
<add><ab facs="#facs_33_line_1576652619684_1430">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd auch
                                    <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab><ab facs="#facs_33_line_1576652622552_1435">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>kauffl<ex>eute</ex></expan> gen
                                            <expan>frankf<ex>urt</ex></expan></del></ab><ab facs="#facs_33_line_1576652625645_1440">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>eygenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab></add> wiſſen / ſo Jr
                        ſchıerſt mügt / daʒ wir <del rend="strikethrough"> vnd ſie </del> vns
                        darnach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l34">wiſſen cʒu rihten / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_33_r1l35"><expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan> <expan>Swacʒenberg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_33_r1l36"><expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>ſi<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_33" id="15r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Moriczen Auracher und <expan>Heinr<ex>ichen</ex></expan> Frauhofern,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern czu Wertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist fürware gesagt und czu wissen getan
                        worden, wie daz gar grosz gewerb und <expan>samnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> in
                        Francken und danyden ümb sey. Begern wir von euch, daz ir an dem hauptman,
                        der euch <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, und auch an
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>wo ir mügt</add> in geheime <expan>vorsch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet,
                        wer das gewerb also tu und waz das gewerbe sey und auf wen und waz ir also
                        ervorschett oder erfaret, das lat uns wissen so ir schierst mügt, daz wir
                        uns darnach wissen czu rihten. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan>
<expan>Swaczenberg<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
